U. D. DAVIDSON & CO.
Direct Importers and Manufacturers of Human Hair and Hair and Hairwear.

Let us interest you with the business. You are a businessman and you want to sell human hair goods. Son and we need an office in your town and a store in human hair goods. You need us. We will send you this latest line of human hair goods which consists of 1 Switch, motion that goes entirely around the head, 1 large box of Cluster Puffs, 1 set of Front Bange, 1 set of Beautiful Clusters. These goods are made out of the best human hair that the store has. The switch is 20 inches long, thick and heavy;

Finest and largest colored hotel in America. First-class accommodations for married and single people. Everything new and up-to-date.

Rooms, by day, 60c, 75c and $1.00;
By Week, $2.00 and up.
